  "text": "Classification: For classification, we use Linear Support Vector Machine (LSVM) [CITATION_1] as the classifier. Leave-onesubject-out cross-validation (LOSOCV) method is adopted to determine the penalty parameter c in SVM. For each test subject, LOSOCV is applied to the training samples, where in each fold the samples belonging to one subject are served as validation set and the rest of samples compose the new training set to select the best c and the selected c is used for testing.",
